lities by allowing for Multi-Factor-Authentication (MFA) within the IAM solution. Simplifying the integration of IAM and MFA not only provides our clients with additional security but it also provides OverWatchID with stickiness when clients that are looking for an IAM solution exclusively.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Focus for The Team in the near future will be on enhancing The Platform for ease of implementation. While performing implementations and POC’s for clients we have been able to identify nuances to how clients are using The Platform. Some of the use cases have been repeated by multiple clients and make sense to integrate with the product for future clients to use as well as a for a goodwill gesture to our current client base. Showing ability to adapt is a strong suit of The Team and has been recognized by our clients.</p></div></div><div class=\"x_update-html-section\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(74, 75, 77); color: rgb(74, 75, 77); font-family: Whitney, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; text-size-adjust: auto; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 22px; margin: 30px 0px 8px;\"><b style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">STAFFING &amp; TEAM:&nbsp;</b></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">We are preparing three offer letters for additional hires in the Development team, two full-time hires, and one intern and expect to finalize within the first few weeks of July.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\"><i style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><b style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">Please note all information provided within is confidential to the company, and should not be distributed outside of the intended list of recipients</b></i></p></div>','PUBLISH','News from Andy Funk'),(47,14,'2018-07-07','<p><font size=\"6\" color=\"#cccccc\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;\">Key Metrics for June</font></p><div style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: wf_segoe-ui_normal, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;\">Revenue up 91% (yr/yr):&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;\">65k to 126k&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: wf_segoe-ui_normal, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;\">Felt Plus Subscribers up 17%:&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;\">2,650 to 3,100</span><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: wf_segoe-ui_normal, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;\">Felt Pro Subscribers up 13%:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;\">350 to 394</span><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: wf_segoe-ui_normal, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;\">14-16 months run way (expected to become profitable within this time)</span><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: wf_segoe-ui_normal, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;\">Total registered users up 400% growth (yr/yr): 60,000 to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">300,000&nbsp;</span><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: wf_segoe-ui_normal, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;\">Total active emails on our list up 400% (yr/yr):&nbsp; 50,000 to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">216,000</span><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: wf_segoe-ui_normal, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 15px;\"><div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">I expected revenue to grow 65% in June so I\'m very happy. By the end of July, we\'ll have crossed the 600k in revenue for the year. So I think we can hit our goal of crossing the 1M mark for the year by increasing our subscriber base and releasing Felt Holiday Cards.<br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204); font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: small;\"><font size=\"6\" color=\"#cccccc\"><br></font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: small;\"><font size=\"6\" color=\"#cccccc\">T-Mobile Update</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: small;\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: small;\">Our Father\'s Day T-Mobile campaign went off without a hitch. The system was up the entire time and all of the orders were mailed on time. Here are some stats:</div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: small;\"><ul><li>85,000 total cards mailed</li><li>30% of users we got from Mother\'s Day T-Mobile came back on Father\'s Day</li></ul><div>T-Mobile is very happy and has awarded us the December campaign! We will be working out the exact date soon.</div></div></span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204); font-size: xx-large;\">Plan to Grow Subscription</span><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">Our current subscription plan is a \"use it or lose it\" model. We surveyed our users and over half of the recent people who recently canceled cited this as the reason.&nbsp;<br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">We chose the use it or lose it model because if users sent all three cards in a month, we lost about $2. Under our new fulfillment rates we always make money.&nbsp;<br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">Under our new model your subscription fee will be credited to your account, for months you don\'t use the app. This opens a lot of re-marketing opportunities.<br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">We have 3,100 active subscribers and about 7,000 who are canceled.<br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">Our end of year goals are:</div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\"><ol><li>6,000 active subscribers</li><li>2% churn</li><li>$100 LTV</li></ol></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204); font-size: xx-large;\">Felt Holiday Cards</span><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">If we get 5,000 people to send 50 cards each this holiday season at $2 a card, we\'ll generate $500,000 in revenue and net $300,000.</div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">We\'ve done extensive surveys and believe that we have a 10,000 - 20,000 people in our addressable market (aka. people on our email list that send holiday cards).<br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">We are targeting to be live by the end of October.&nbsp;<br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">This project will also allow us to release Invitations, Announcements, Postcards, and custom stationery in early 2019.</div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\"><font color=\"#cccccc\" size=\"6\">Key Hires</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\"><div><br></div><div>We brought on Stephanie Gelabert as Creative Director. Stephanie was the Design Director at our old design firm and was named a 2017 top 50 designer in the country. She\'s been working on Felt for the last five years so we couldn\'t be happier that she\'s now leading our design efforts.</div></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\">We\'re actively interviewing for a Head of Engineering too! We\'re looking for someone who has experience at a consumer tech product company. Someone who has 10+ years of experience as an application architect. Someone who has experience with scale and who\'s looking to get their hands dirty helping to build and scale our products. If you know anyone, please email me. Thank you!!</div></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: small;\"><div><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204); font-size: xx-large;\">Our Plan</span><br></div><div><br></div><div>We are going to focus on revenue and product growth the remainder of the year. Then release viral technology by Q2 2019.&nbsp;</div><div>I believe this plan puts us on a path to being profitable by holidays 2019 and positions us to better execute our really big ideas!<br></div><div>Please let me know if you\'d like to chat about the details.</div><div><div><font size=\"6\" color=\"#cccccc\">Fundraising Update</font></div><div><br></div><div>We\'ve closed $740,000 out of the 1M we\'re raising. I expect us to close the entire round very soon. We will then have about 14 - 16 months of run way. I expect us to become profitable in that time.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div>','PENDING','June Upadate');
